When you doing a mission with the homie and he perfectly replicates the call of a Prosthemadera novaeseelandiae, otherwise known as the Tui native to New Zealand, and now one of the guards wanna be a bird enthusiast and investigate the sound...

Melodic - Tidiane
Outta My Mind - OmarCameUp
